author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: The Weeknd Unveils New SS17 XO Collection
text:
Visit the original post to see all 28 images from this gallery. 
Ahead of his Starboy world tour which kicks off on Friday in Stockholm, Sweden, The Weeknd this week shares the initial drop from his XO line for 2017.
The merch consists of sweatshirts, jackets, graphic tees and socks, all of which arrive in limited quantities, featuring various XO and The Weeknd-specific branding. The majority of the styles feature either a black and white or a white and red color scheme, as you can get a feel for The Weeknd’s first SS17 delivery via the imagery above.
Be sure to stay locked in to Abel’s web store for purchasing options.
